<title>yạrb ạlʿẓmẗ bnmjdk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- yạrb ạlʿẓmẗ bnmjdk nnsẖd wbṣwt msmwʿ
 mʿ kl nsmẗ bnsbḥk wbnkrm ạsm yswʿ
 1- kl qlwbnạ tgẖny sẖʿbk byk mthny
 frḥtnạ byk yạ fạdynạ rạysnạ wmlk lynạ
 ḥq wwạjb ʿlynạ nkrm ạ̹sm yswʿ
 2- tbqy̱ ḥyạtnạ dẖbyḥẗ nʿysẖhạ lyk tsbyḥẗ
 nhtf nʿly gẖnạnạ wạldnyạ dy smʿạnạ
 nfḍl lḥd lqạỷnạ nkrm ạsm yswʿ</lyrics>
</song>